{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Installation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Install ReaPack.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab On REAPER main menu, "Extensions > ReaPack > Import repositories..."\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Write {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/pelori/PeloReaper/raw/master/index.xml"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
index.xml
}}}
 URL, press "OK" button. https://github.com/pelori/PeloReaper/raw/master/index.xml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab "Extensions > ReaPack > Browse packages..." then type "PeloReaper". Right-click "PeloReaper Extension" package, Select "Install vXXXX.XX.XX".\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 5.\tx360\tab Don't forget quit Browse packages window with pressing "OK" button.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 6.\tx360\tab Quit and Restart REAPER.\sa180\par}
